{"title":"珠江盆地〔外两首〕","authors":["陈忠干"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":2,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠江盆地〔外两首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈忠干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠江口盆地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸脯说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有很多财富、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很多财富！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁勇敢，来耕耘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁爱我，来开拓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是他的银行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一口掏不尽的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金库银锅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要是空话连篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要是不懂科学；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我只有给他："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一船泥沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身泡沫！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试油歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“采油树”上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓烟滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛丛丛绿叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡荡袅袅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把汗的种籽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播进南海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻工在笑看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光的美妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一团团鲜红的火球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是累累的果实在摇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这话也算说得对"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥部最高指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战在基层岗位。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上滑，他递过垫布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天气热，他送来汽水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井台缺员，他作记录，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶边人少，他忙帮炊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台风袭来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命令职工撤退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己却毅然留下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担当平台警卫……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人开玩笑说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“他捧工人的大腿！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他听了哈哈大笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这话也算说得对……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}